  "body": "Getting rid of any kind of punishment for late reveals makes most sense when the custody period has the same length as the reveal deadlines. Therefore we should change to\r\n\r\n * Custody periods of 2^14 epochs\r\n * Reveal deadline: Another round of 2^14 epochs\r\n * Chunk challenge/custody slashing deadline: [This could be either 2^11/2^14 epochs]",
